      "series_name": "GT7100 Series",
      "brand_name": "3M",
      "category_name": "",
      "product_description": "3M Acrylic Foam Tape GT7100 Series offers very good adhesion performance and high flexibility. These tapes are specifically designed for the attachment of automotive exterior and interior trim applications.",
      "product_features": "Provides final adhesion and holding power to automotive paints and substrates\nMeets a number of OEM specifications\nFollows shrinkage and elongation of plastic parts caused by temperature change and has good stress relaxation properties\nViscoelastic core conforms well to complex geometries and delivers excellent wet out\nDemonstrates excellent adhesive performance at various temperature conditions\nExcels in a variety of weather conditions and offers solvent and high temperature resistance",
      "main_applications": "Attachment of automotive exterior trim applications\nAttachment of automotive interior trim applications",
      "special_applications": "Construction summary: red polyethylene liner / acrylic pressure sensitive adhesive / acrylic foam / acrylic pressure sensitive adhesive.\nAn extended liner tab is recommended. Consult application guidelines for detailed product use instructions.\nTypical performance values depend on substrate characteristics and/or paint composition and are for reference only, not for specification purposes; certificate of analysis should be used for specification values.\nShelf life is three years from date of manufacture when stored at 23°C +/-2°C and 50% +/-4% RH. Short uncontrolled transport periods should not impact performance, but extended storage beyond recommended conditions is not advised.",
      "source_page": null,
      "source_text": null,
